      "pointerTo": 6914.1,
      "helpText": "This field can no longer be changed by an FC Document because the CMR now determines the cost center and only FR Documents can change a cost center.   Basis for LOCATION (as in department locator).   CMRs that are assigned to a station other than the owning station for this asset are unacceptable. A change of this kind will require you to enter an FD document, then edit the CMR, and then enter an FA document. ",
